Parameters:
    Sensor Range (int) - how far to scan for targets
    Command Radius (int) - how far I will scan for other ships who I can command, or be commanded by (formation check distance)
    Fleet Separation (int) - how far I will move away from the commander in my fleet
    Max Distance (int) -
    Location (list) - the locations I will go to (defined places or coordinates)
        object location
        coordinate list (including single coordinate location)
